snippet.title: Best VGM 1320 - MediEvil : Resurrection - End Titles
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PSP
MediEvil : Resurrection (2005)
End Titles
Bob & Barn, City of Prague Philharmonic Orchestra
